{"tid":712070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9個月大B女跌落床　疑被單纏腳倒吊窒息致命","createTime":"2018-06-22T00:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T03:49:44.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0e521e86ce472a31ce0a3ce4d42c2c69d70383","tid":712070,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"屯門良景邨良萃樓9個月大女嬰意外跌落床昏迷，送院搶救後不治。消息稱，昨晚8時許，女嬰的祖父及外傭在家中，女嬰放在房間一張雙人床上獨自睡覺，床邊放有枕頭圍住，而地上則置有床褥，女嬰當時並無異樣。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180621/photo/bkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180622051238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180621%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180622051238&h=0b925fc1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n但一小時後，女嬰被發現已跌落床，側身躺在地上的床褥，陷入昏迷，腳纏有被單，女嬰送院後證實死亡。消息指，事發房間裝有閉路電視，警方翻查錄影，發現事發時女嬰睡醒，爬過床邊枕頭跌落床，腳遭被單纏住，倒吊了一段時間，才跌落地上床褥，因此，不排除女嬰倒吊時窒息致命，警方調查後認為事件並無可疑，但確實死因仍有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180621/bkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180621%2Fbkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001.html&d=afgieTsPw%2F151FGscSvHiwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e0c52148\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180621/bkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d04fa9714273405c8f575569b12225e25d59e83a","tid":712070,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:49:44.000Z","msg":"與女嬰一家相熟的街坊對此感到非常難過，並指B女非常可愛，一雙眼睛大大，每逢外出，父母也喜歡為她悉心打扮。由於B女「唔鍾意瞓BB床，每次瞓落去都會喊」，故懷疑父母將她放在大人床睡覺時出事。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180621/photo/bkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180622051238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180621%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180622051238&h=538cf6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">女嬰家人獲噩耗後非常傷心。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180621/photo/bkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180622051238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180621%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180621103730136-0621_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180622051238&h=d2a993ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現場為良萃樓一單位。</span></div>"},{"pid":"85e72399070b9cef8665c281eee62ab3a878ed59","tid":712070,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"9個月大識爬黎爬去<br />\n呢個時候先要放喺bb床最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲由佢喺大床爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6860763df8be847ef7b65d5b7202e91c0066c6bd","tid":712070,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"85e72399070b9cef8665c281eee62ab3a878ed59","tid":712070,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"9個月大識爬黎爬去<br />\n呢個時候先要放喺bb床最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲由佢喺大床爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:57:26.000Z","msg":"其實佢有錢買bb床應該唔會放佢係大床"},{"pid":"a852bb777cec7c98ba5bbc34f64b7fa80f5ef3c0","tid":712070,"uid":55614,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6860763df8be847ef7b65d5b7202e91c0066c6bd","tid":712070,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"85e72399070b9cef8665c281eee62ab3a878ed59","tid":712070,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"9個月大識爬黎爬去<br />\n呢個時候先要放喺bb床最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲由佢喺大床爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite